Intel Mobile:
GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="acpi_osi=Linux pcie_aspm=force drm.vblankoffdelay=1 i915.enable_guc=2 scsi_mod.use_blk_mq=1 intel_iommu=on"


Intel Desktop:
GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="acpi_osi=Linux scsi_mod.use_blk_mq=1"


AMD Desktop:
GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="acpi_osi=Linux acpi_enforce_resources=lax scsi_mod.use_blk_mq=1"


Monitor resolution setting for nvidia card:
GRUB_GFXMODE="1920x1080"
GRUB_GFXPAYLOAD_LINUX=keep


IOMMU for Intel:
intel_iommu=on


IOMMU for AMD:
amd_iommu=on iommu=pt


Disable Spectre, Meltdown, L1TF and Other CPU Mitigations
mitigations=off
